export enum FlexBoxAlignItems { /** * Items are aligned toward the start of the flex-direction.
* Note: Corresponds to `flex-start`. */ Start = 'Start', /** * Items are centered.
* Note: Corresponds to `center`. */ Center = 'Center', /** * Items are aligned toward the end of the flex-direction.
* Note: Corresponds to `flex-end`. */ End = 'End', /** * Items are aligned by their baseline.
* Note: Corresponds to `baseline`. */ Baseline = 'Baseline', /** * Items are stretched to fill the container.
* Note: Corresponds to `stretch`. */ Stretch = 'Stretch' }
